Congratulations to you all!!

We hope you had a great weekend of sport and fun.....thanks to all who played!!

The Awards for the 27th Australian Corporate Games were presented at the Pullman & Mercure Albert Park during the Games Award Party. We had a fantastic night so many thanks to the Pullman & Mercure...

For the record we had 8,137 participants from 340 organisations competing over the 3 days of competition. ANZ again entered the largest team with 747 participants.

The Games Results are now available from the right hand tile on this page.

Information on the 2020 Games will be up by May. The weekend of November 20-22 has now been confirmed.
